  "promptForAI": "Create a complete manual brew coffee timer web application for 'Elixir Beans - for coffee adventurers' using only HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The app should support both V60 and Hario Switch brewing methods with the Elixir Beans brand identity featuring a vintage badge aesthetic, mystical/magical theme, and deep purple (#6B3A7C) and cream (#F4E4C1) color scheme.\n\nDesign System Requirements:\n- Use deep purple as primary color for all interactive elements and branding\n- Apply cream/beige backgrounds for cards and sections\n- Include orange/gold gradients for CTAs and important actions\n- Add decorative elements: four-pointed stars, halftone dot patterns, concentric ring borders\n- Incorporate elixir bottle/coffee pot iconography throughout\n- Maintain badge-style circular elements inspired by the logo\n- Use 'Enchantment Series' aesthetic with mystical, apothecary-inspired design\n\nBrewing Methods to Include:\n1. V60 Recipes:\n   - James Hoffmann Classic Method\n   - Tetsu Kasuya 4:6 Method\n   - Martin Wölfl 2024 World Champion (OREA V4/V60 alternative)\n   - Carlos Medina 2023 World Champion (Origami/V60)\n\n2. Hario Switch Recipes:\n   - Tetsu Kasuya Hybrid Method (immersion + percolation)\n   - Simple Immersion Method (beginner-friendly)\n   - Hybrid Bloom Method (sweetness + clarity)\n\nKey Features:\n- Recipe selector with brewer type filter (V60 / Switch)\n- Multi-phase brew timer with circular badge-style progress indicator\n- Switch position indicator (for Switch recipes only) showing closed/open state\n- Phase-based guidance with automatic transitions\n- Brew history with local storage\n- Settings for customizing coffee weight and ratio\n- Mobile-first, responsive interface\n\nImplement smooth animations with magical sparkle effects on completion, be fully accessible (WCAG AA), and feel like a native mobile app with vintage coffee adventure theming. Prioritize user experience during brewing with minimal interactions and clear visual feedback. Use CSS variables for Elixir Beans design tokens throughout.\n\nCritical Brand Elements:\n- Elixir Beans circular logo/badge in header\n- 'for coffee adventurers' tagline\n- Purple and cream color dominance\n- Decorative stars at phase completions\n- Vintage badge styling on timer and important elements\n- Warm, inviting, mystical atmosphere\n- Champion recipe badges/indicators for world champion methods"
}